MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping used to load EXTERNAL_NET_DEMAND for particular customer_cd
MAPPING.NAME: m_EXT_NET_DMD_HAA

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Acts as a safe expression before target to avoid data type discrepancy
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_EXT_NET_DMD

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: concat( concat( concat( concat('FCST', ' '), FISCAL_YEAR), ' '), FISCAL_WEEK)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: DEMAND_SOURCE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on PACK to get PACKAGE_QTY
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_PACK

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF.PLANT_CD as PLANT_CD, EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF.EXTERNAL_PLANT as EXTERNAL_PLANT FROM EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup to get SCHEDULE_RUN and CUSTOMER_CD
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_CUST_HEADER

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ holds data from source HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR.FISCAL_YEAR, HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR.FISCAL_MONTH, HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR.FISCAL_WEEK FROM HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ holds data from source DBA_GROSS_CAPACITY_FORECAST
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_DBA_GROSS_CAPACITY_FORECAST

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.ITEM_ID, A.FISCAL_YEAR, A.FISCAL_WEEK, A.FROM_DATE, A.TO_DATE, A.CUST_SHIP_FROM_DC, A.FISCAL_PERIOD, A.REGULAR_SALES_QTY, A.DIV_CODE FROM DBA_GROSS_CAPACITY_FORECAST A WHERE A.item_id is not null and A.regular_sales_qty > 0

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on STYLE to get PACK_CD
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STYLE.PACK_CD as PACK_CD, STYLE.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD FROM STYLE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joiner to combine data based on year,period and week
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_DBA_HBI_FIS_CAL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: FISCAL_YEAR = HBI_FISCAL_YEAR AND FISCAL_WEEK = HBI_FISCAL_WEEK AND FISCAL_PERIOD = HBI_FISCAL_MONTH

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ holds data from source EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.CUSTOMER_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.EXTERNAL_SKU, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.ITEM_ID, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.SELLING_STYLE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.SELLING_COLOR_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.SELLING_SIZE_CD, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.SELLING_REVISION_NO, EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joine to combine DBA_GROSS_CAPACITY_FORECAST data with CODES_TABLE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_DBA_CODES

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To filter rows which match the required condition.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FL_WEEK_BEGIN_DT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joiner to combine DBA_GROSS_CAPACITY_FORECAST amd EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_DBA_GRS_EXT_SKU

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ to fetch data from CODES_TABLE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_CODES_TABLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LTRIM(RTRIM(CODES_TABLE.CODE)) FROM CODES_TABLE CODES_TABLE WHERE CODES_TABLE.CATEGORY = 'EDC' AND SHORT_DESCRIPTION=$$CUSTOMER_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR to get week_begin_date
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_HBI_FIS_CALENDAR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT '1' as DUMMY, HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR.WEEK_BEGIN_DATE as WEEK_BEGIN_DATE FROM HBI_FISCAL_CALENDAR WHERE TRUNC(CALENDAR_DATE)=TRUNC(SYSDATE)
